{"tid":2334938,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"羅冠聰: 身處海外 我唯一能回報香港的只有永無休止地向政權纏鬥","createTime":"2020-12-21T12:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T13:59:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":52,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"022fa0ec58bfdd70fdc932d214828eb16b9a45ec","tid":2334938,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"冬至是一家人喜慶地聚會的日子，準備迎接寒流到來。來到2020年的香港，對很多人而言，能夠與家人團聚已是奢侈：城內被囚禁的、城外流浪異鄉的，無不惦念著團聚的時光，以及在「正常」日子的點滴。<br />\n當然，我也會掛念香港的一切，以及仍在鐵柵後的諸位同伴手足。然而，官媒喉舌將我列為國安法下的通緝犯，已印證了香港一日被暴政籠罩，我也無法重回我的家鄉。而日後若要續領香港特區護照，便必須進入中國大使館辦理手續，與「自動送中」無異，也許當時我便立刻被中共「法辦」了。<br />\n假若我再不行動，我就只能成為一個沒有護照、身份的人。經歷一連串思想掙扎後，我決定在英國申請政治庇護（Asylum Seeking），成為流散在全球各地的其中一位香港人。也許大家早在新聞報道中看到英國嚴謹且高門檻的政治庇護審批，我作為其中一位擁有媒體資源的流亡者，我和其他申請者都會走過同一樣的程序，了解到當中的繁複以及問題。這個經歷令我更能向英國政府就如何便利香港手足提供意見，並再次透過我的個案來引起英國政界上下對香港流亡者的關注。目前在我的倡議工作中，如何能令在英國的手足、香港人得到更適切的援助，佔據了很重要的部份。<br />\n無論身在何方，我永遠都不會放棄香港人的身份，也會為這個代表著意志、勇敢、追求自由的身份而自豪。而香港人面對強權的戰鬥，亦不會因為我們被逼離開家鄉而止息。身處海外，我唯一能回報香港的只有永無休止地向政權纏鬥。縱使天空依然黑暗，我們仍不能熄滅內心的火光。希望在世界各地的手足都在冬至平安，凝聚成更重要的力量，守護著香港的文化、價值。<br />\n英國衛報投稿文章：I left Hong Kong for London so I could tell Britain the truth about China <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/dec/21/hong-kong-london-uk-eu-china-asulum\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fcommentisfree%2F2020%2Fdec%2F21%2Fhong-kong-london-uk-eu-china-asulum&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzProWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=53f6f24a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2020/dec/21/hong-kong-london-uk-eu-china-asulum</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2430227677128551\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FNathanLawKC%2Fposts%2F2430227677128551&d=Yr0hxYoWOJ9ZaoTMuy4WzProWj9UcGxh4mdojqPZn1M%3D&h=e758d92d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/NathanLawKC/posts/2430227677128551</a>"},{"pid":"2c8a140e5846b115735f5c3ad2bddd45a49bbdd2","tid":2334938,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e38c0cbdbb6570a7ce40688b5b93007703f025ee","tid":2334938,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c8a140e5846b115735f5c3ad2bddd45a49bbdd2","tid":2334938,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:54:04.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872fbb4760b7bbaf2ff50b1b08df3c2043939cf3","tid":2334938,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10e348f5006c2888dfc02c85d547b7ff26b832e","tid":2334938,"uid":76804,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:55:11.000Z","msg":"要放棄香港一切<br />\n屋企人朋友<br />\n真係唔容易<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb0e9c09dba9c3e418a07abb3e7991f25bfd189d","tid":2334938,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T12:55:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c4de32b4f799eb9e84b9b3aa90969f6aa4c0358","tid":2334938,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"